title: Lakewood Rental
posting_body: ['Beautiful house on a nice lot in Tacoma!', 'This charmer has TONS to offer-3 Beds, 2.5 Bath with extra space upstairs to use as office or multipurpose room!', 'New appliances, white cabinets, LVP flooring throughout, new hot water heater, exterior paint.', 'Current additional family room could be changed back to main dining room.', 'Plus 10X20 outdoor shed that is wired and sheet rocked - lots of possibilities!', 'Central and close to all amenities!', 'Check out the patio, too!', 'Get approved quickly so you can live in this beautiful home.', 'In order to qualify for the Rent To Own Program:', '• You must have at least $85,000 in Combined Gross Household Income', '•', 'A minimum FICO score of 620', '• No evictions in the past 3 years', '• Takes 5-6 weeks from start to finish', 'We work with previous bankruptcies, foreclosures and short sales!', 'There is a 1 time $75 application fee, which is good for the whole household, and for any of our qualifying houses!', 'You must be pre-approved to view any available properties.', 'Pet Friendly!', 'Up to 3 cats/dogs OKAY!', '(Due to extreme insurance liability, we cannot allow Dobermans, Pitbulls, Rottweilers or Mastiffs)', 'Contact me today for more information and details about the program!', "The home in the picture is an example of what you could get, it's not this home in particular.", '•\tdo NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers', 'Kristin Hood', 'Keller Williams Lake Tapps']
